<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 04:08:01 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>防止西岸战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-02/ty-article-opinion/.premium/preventing-war-in-the-west-bank/0000018b-8c72-db7e-af9b-eff3d04e0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 02:12:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-02/ty-article-opinion/.premium/preventing-war-in-the-west-bank/0000018b-8c72-db7e-af9b-eff3d04e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列从加沙撤出战略尚未被采纳</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-02/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-exit-strategy-from-gaza-that-hasnt-been-adopted/0000018b-8c23-d46b-a18f-8cfb36d20000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 02:09:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-02/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-exit-strategy-from-gaza-that-hasnt-been-adopted/0000018b-8c23-d46b-a18f-8cfb36d20000</guid></item><item><title>这些是加沙贾巴利亚难民营遭到轰炸后被救出的儿童</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-02/ty-article-opinion/.premium/these-are-the-children-extracted-after-the-bombardment-of-gazas-jabalya-refugee-camp/0000018b-8c23-d46b-a18f-8cfb57690000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 01:44:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-02/ty-article-opinion/.premium/these-are-the-children-extracted-after-the-bombardment-of-gazas-jabalya-refugee-camp/0000018b-8c23-d46b-a18f-8cfb57690000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防部长：立即向巴勒斯坦当局转移资金；哈马斯指挥官在以色列国防军空袭中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article-live/11-israeli-soldiers-killed-as-idf-expands-gaza-ground-operation/0000018b-8925-d055-afbf-bba702e90000</link><description>自加沙地面行动开始以来，已有 16 名以色列士兵丧生 ■ 也门胡塞武装发动远程导弹和无人机袭击后，以色列军舰部署在红海作为增援部队 ■ 以色列空袭杀死了哈马斯贾巴利亚旅指挥官和 10 月 7 日大屠杀中的一名领导人易卜拉欣·比亚里 (Ibrahim Biari) ■ 哈马斯管理的卫生部：8,000 多名巴勒斯坦人被杀 ■ 240 名人质在加沙被扣押，40 人仍然失踪 ■ 至少 1,300 名平民和士兵在哈马斯大屠杀中丧生</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 00:24:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article-live/11-israeli-soldiers-killed-as-idf-expands-gaza-ground-operation/0000018b-8925-d055-afbf-bba702e90000</guid></item><item><title>为了应对日益增长的压力，哥伦比亚大学和宾夕法尼亚大学宣布打击反犹太主义的计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/responding-to-growing-pressure-columbia-and-penn-announce-plans-to-combat-antisemitism/0000018b-8cb7-db7e-af9b-eff725b10000</link><description>自10月7日哈马斯入侵以色列以来，两所大学一直面临来自犹太教师、学生和校友的压力，要求解决犹太学生的安全问题</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Nov 2023 22:34:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/responding-to-growing-pressure-columbia-and-penn-announce-plans-to-combat-antisemitism/0000018b-8cb7-db7e-af9b-eff725b10000</guid></item><item><title>对于以色列人来说，加沙长期血腥战争的现实正在击中要害</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-01/ty-article/.premium/for-israelis-the-reality-of-a-long-bloody-war-in-gaza-is-hitting-home/0000018b-8bf6-db7e-af9b-ebf78b290000</link><description>加沙战争不会是冲向明确胜利线的冲刺，而是一场漫长而混乱的马拉松。以色列公众希望跑步者的脚不会像不久前那样陷入难处理的泥浆中</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Nov 2023 19:25:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-01/ty-article/.premium/for-israelis-the-reality-of-a-long-bloody-war-in-gaza-is-hitting-home/0000018b-8bf6-db7e-af9b-ebf78b290000</guid></item><item><title>美国认为巴勒斯坦权力机构是加沙问题的可能解决方案，但以色列正在努力削弱它</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/.premium/u-s-sees-palestinian-authority-as-possible-solution-in-gaza-as-israel-works-to-weaken-it/0000018b-8b8a-db7e-af9b-ebcb50e30000</link><description>尽管由总统马哈茂德·阿巴斯领导的陷入困境的约旦河西岸机构得到了拜登政府的支持，但极右翼的以色列部长们却试图扣留对该机构的资助</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Nov 2023 17:12:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/.premium/u-s-sees-palestinian-authority-as-possible-solution-in-gaza-as-israel-works-to-weaken-it/0000018b-8b8a-db7e-af9b-ebcb50e30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列议会极右翼成员兹维·苏科特将担任约旦河西岸小组委员会主席</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/.premium/far-right-israeli-knesset-member-zvi-sukkot-to-head-subcommittee-on-the-west-bank/0000018b-8b93-db71-a7df-ffdfd1ea0000</link><description>住棚节年轻时属于宗教犹太复国主义党，曾因涉嫌参与西岸犹太极端主义活动而成为辛贝特安全部门的目标</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Nov 2023 16:20:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/.premium/far-right-israeli-knesset-member-zvi-sukkot-to-head-subcommittee-on-the-west-bank/0000018b-8b93-db71-a7df-ffdfd1ea0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯官员：我们将重复10月7日的袭击，直到以色列被歼灭</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/hamas-official-we-will-repeat-october-7-attacks-until-israel-is-annihilated/0000018b-8b9d-db7e-af9b-ebdfbee90000</link><description>哈马斯官员加齐·哈马德告诉黎巴嫩电视台，以色列的存在是所有暴力和痛苦的根源</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Nov 2023 16:10:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/hamas-official-we-will-repeat-october-7-attacks-until-israel-is-annihilated/0000018b-8b9d-db7e-af9b-ebdfbee90000</guid></item><item><title>数百人参与袭击阿拉伯人和左翼分子，但以色列警方只逮捕了四人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-made-only-four-arrests-despite-hundreds-of-attacks-on-arabs-and-leftists/0000018b-8ad0-dce3-afaf-affa24af0000</link><description>警方发言人表示，尽管许多事件都有警察在场，并且一些事件有视频证据，但“事件仍在继续调查，目的是找出更多嫌疑人”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Nov 2023 14:51:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-made-only-four-arrests-despite-hundreds-of-attacks-on-arabs-and-leftists/0000018b-8ad0-dce3-afaf-affa24af0000</guid></item><item><title>黑暗中的拍摄：《国土报》摄影师也加入了这场战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/shots-in-the-dark-haaretz-photographers-turned-into-war-photojournalists-overnight/0000018b-858b-dd28-a7df-959f95fe0000</link><description>记录以色列-哈马斯战争：我们跟随五位《国土报》摄影师，追求展示战争的恐怖，但并未实际展示它</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Nov 2023 13:43:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/shots-in-the-dark-haaretz-photographers-turned-into-war-photojournalists-overnight/0000018b-858b-dd28-a7df-959f95fe0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙发生重大停电后，广泛的互联网和电话服务已恢复</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/widespread-internet-and-phone-services-restored-after-major-outages-in-gaza/0000018b-8a43-d466-a9ab-becbb74a0000</link><description>虽然通讯已开始恢复，但红十字会表示，这种停电扰乱了急救人员的工作，并使平民更难寻求安全。上周末，在以色列的猛烈轰炸中，加沙大部分地区的手机和互联网服务突然消失</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Nov 2023 12:47:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/widespread-internet-and-phone-services-restored-after-major-outages-in-gaza/0000018b-8a43-d466-a9ab-becbb74a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列没有在加沙实施种族灭绝</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-01/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-is-not-committing-genocide-in-gaza/0000018b-8785-d055-afbf-b7a75d450000</link><description>关于以色列在加沙实施种族灭绝以报复哈马斯 10 月 7 日大屠杀的说法是一个错误的说法，没有国际法依据。这是一种危险的干扰，更有可能导致加沙、以色列及其他地区更多平民死亡</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Nov 2023 12:22:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-01/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-is-not-committing-genocide-in-gaza/0000018b-8785-d055-afbf-b7a75d450000</guid></item><item><title>哀悼中，以色列定居点工程庆祝伟大胜利</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-01/ty-article-opinion/.premium/amid-the-mourning-israels-settlement-enterprise-celebrates-a-great-victory/0000018b-85a6-dd28-a7df-95b7f9520000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Nov 2023 12:05:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-01/ty-article-opinion/.premium/amid-the-mourning-israels-settlement-enterprise-celebrates-a-great-victory/0000018b-85a6-dd28-a7df-95b7f9520000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦卫生部：有特殊需要的男子在约旦河西岸被以色列军队击毙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-health-ministry-man-with-special-needs-shot-dead-by-israeli-army-in-west-bank/0000018b-8a64-dce3-afaf-af6e7f3e0000</link><description>目击者称，65 岁的马吉德·阿瓦德 (Majid Awad) 在一次以色列国防军行动中在街上闲逛时被一名狙击手射杀。另外三名武装人员在杰宁被以色列国防军杀害</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Nov 2023 11:35:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-health-ministry-man-with-special-needs-shot-dead-by-israeli-army-in-west-bank/0000018b-8a64-dce3-afaf-af6e7f3e0000</guid></item><item><title>第一批外国人从加沙穿越拉法边境前往埃及</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/first-group-of-foreign-nationals-crosses-rafah-border-from-gaza-to-egypt/0000018b-8a82-d570-a99b-9aaab3c80000</link><description>在卡塔尔斡旋埃及、以色列和哈马斯之间达成协议后，周三，多达 500 名外国护照持有者将通过从加沙前往埃及的拉法过境点。消息人士称，此次开放与人质问题和人道主义停火等问题无关</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Nov 2023 11:31:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/first-group-of-foreign-nationals-crosses-rafah-border-from-gaza-to-egypt/0000018b-8a82-d570-a99b-9aaab3c80000</guid></item><item><title>女儿被谋杀的以色列科技巨头：“我们不会与哈马斯和平相处，但也许会与阿巴斯和平相处”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/tech-giant-whose-daughter-was-murdered-we-wont-make-peace-with-hamas-maybe-with-abbas/0000018b-861f-df47-a3df-fe1f66dc0000</link><description>10 月 7 日，Mellanox 创始人 Eyal Waldman 和她的伴侣的小女儿被哈马斯谋杀。这位在加沙建立发展中心的企业家仍然梦想和平并呼吁内塔尼亚胡辞职</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Nov 2023 11:07:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/tech-giant-whose-daughter-was-murdered-we-wont-make-peace-with-hamas-maybe-with-abbas/0000018b-861f-df47-a3df-fe1f66dc0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯表示将在“几天内”释放非以色列人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/.premium/hamas-says-it-will-free-non-israeli-hostages-within-days/0000018b-89fa-d805-a98f-bdfb0f6f0000</link><description>如果发生的话，释放任何外国人质并不是以色列和哈马斯之间任何已宣布协议的一部分，但可能是伊朗外交部长访问卡塔尔期间达成的谅解的产物</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Nov 2023 10:46:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/.premium/hamas-says-it-will-free-non-israeli-hostages-within-days/0000018b-89fa-d805-a98f-bdfb0f6f0000</guid></item><item><title>也门点燃的火柴可能迫使沙特阿拉伯和美国采取立场</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/.premium/the-match-lit-in-yemen-may-force-saudi-arabia-and-the-u-s-to-take-a-stance/0000018b-88a9-d055-afbf-baab36290000</link><description>胡塞武装发射弹道导弹和无人机并未对以色列构成直接战略威胁。但它们可能会在其他方面产生影响，其中最主要的是：正常化和沙特与美国的防务协定</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Nov 2023 10:38:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/.premium/the-match-lit-in-yemen-may-force-saudi-arabia-and-the-u-s-to-take-a-stance/0000018b-88a9-d055-afbf-baab36290000</guid></item><item><title>布林肯为加沙援助提出了强有力的理由，称人道主义暂停“必须考虑”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/blinken-makes-forceful-case-for-gaza-aid-says-humanitarian-pauses-must-be-considered/0000018b-8a38-ddfb-a78f-fe3bd45f0000</link><description>美国国务卿在《华盛顿邮报》发表的一篇专栏文章中写道，“我们不必在保卫以色列和援助巴勒斯坦平民之间做出选择。”他还重申两国解决方案是“实现持久和平的唯一可行途径”</description><pubDate>Wed, 01 Nov 2023 10:31:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-01/ty-article/blinken-makes-forceful-case-for-gaza-aid-says-humanitarian-pauses-must-be-considered/0000018b-8a38-ddfb-a78f-fe3bd45f0000</guid></item></channel></rss>